Color Palette:

Background: #f0f8ff (Light Blue)
Text: #333333 (Dark Gray)
Navigation: #2196f3 (Light Blue)
Buttons: #007bff (Blue)
Font: Open Sans from Google Fonts (https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Open+Sans)

Structure:

We'll use one HTML file (index.html) for all three pages and have separate sections for each using HTML anchors (<a>) for navigation.

index.html:

HTML
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport"   
 content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>My Simple Website</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;700&display=swap"   
 rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>My Simple Website</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="#home">Home</a>
      <a href="#products">Products</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section id="home">
